# SFX Library Setup Guide

This directory should contain sound effect files for enhancing real estate videos.

## Directory Structure

```
sfx_library/
├── birds.mp3              # Birds chirping sound
├── wind.mp3               # Soft wind/breeze
├── door_open.mp3          # Door opening sound
├── door_close.mp3         # Door closing sound
├── footsteps.mp3          # General footsteps
├── footsteps_wood.mp3     # Footsteps on wooden floor
├── window.mp3             # Window opening sound
├── jazz_light.mp3         # Light jazz background music
├── guitar_ambient.mp3     # Ambient acoustic guitar
├── water.mp3              # Water flowing sound
├── whoosh.mp3             # Transition whoosh effect
└── transition.mp3         # Subtle transition sound
```

## File Requirements

- **Format**: MP3, WAV, or OGG
- **Duration**: 2-10 seconds (will be trimmed if longer)
- **Quality**: 48kHz sample rate recommended
- **Volume**: Original volume will be reduced to 30% in mix

## Free Sound Effect Resources

1. **Freesound.org** - https://freesound.org
2. **Zapsplat** - https://www.zapsplat.com
3. **BBC Sound Effects** - https://sound-effects.bbcrewind.co.uk
4. **Pixabay Audio** - https://pixabay.com/sound-effects

## Usage in Script

The AI script generator can output `audio_cue` fields like:
- "Birds chirping"
- "Soft wind"
- "Door open"
- "Footsteps on wood"

These will be automatically mapped to the corresponding SFX files.

## Enable SFX in Configuration

Set in `.env`:
```bash
SFX_ENABLED=true
SFX_LIBRARY_PATH=/path/to/sfx_library
```
